oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Soil conservation day
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photo from Soil Conservation Day at Bonnie Oaks School, Hamilton County, Tenn. All the men are wearing hats, and three of the men are on tractors. A man shelters himself from the sun with an umbrella on a tractor. Several barns are in the background.
